        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Vera reaches out. Her slightly cold fingertips trace from between your brows, down the bridge of your nose, over your lips, before coming to rest at the most vulnerable part of your neck—where beneath the skin, your carotid artery pulses with the rhythm of life.'}"
